<article class="webring">
    <header class="webring__header">
        <h1 class="webring__title">{{ meta.title }}</h1>
        <p>Politics, just like big corporations, have their own perspective. <br>Politics, just like big corporations, must be well regulated, to keep them from breaking fundamental rules of humanity, generosity, responsibility. </p><p>This webring is a curated list of civil movements working for this goal.</p>
        <a href="mailto:now@civilcontrol.org">Email us!</a>
    </header>
        
    <div class="webring__body">
        <div class="webring__subtitle">
            <h2 class="h3">Members ({{ members | length }})</h2>
            <a href="/feeds.xml" target="_blank">RSS Feeds</a>
        </div>

        <ol class="webring__memberlist">
            {% for member in members %}
            <li class="webring__member">
                <a href="{{ member.url }}" class="webring__link" target="_blank">{{ member.title }}</a>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ol>
    </div>
</article>
